title: Combinators
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Between elements there are some well known structural relations.  Using those relations one could define specific rules to apply styles.

The defined combinators are the following:

* div + p : Adjacent Sibling
* div ~ p : General Sibling
* div > p : Child
* div    p : Descendent